currentdescription: Design, Construction, Supply, Testing, commissioning of Pipe Water Supply Schemes with Electric Driven Pumps and IRON Removal Treatment Plant having Technology (Adsorption/ Nano Technology) of CSIR or certified by CSIR or any other Technology endorsed/ approved by GoI in the IRON affected Left Out Habitations/ Wards of District of Purnea on turn-key basis with 06 months Trial Run after Commissioning and Comprehensive Operation and Maintenance of 60 months after successful completion of Trial Run Period under Mukhyamantri Nishchay (Quality Affected) Yojna on Turn Key basis in ward no. 1,2,7,10 of goriyar west panchayat and ward no. 14 of Dhobgiddha panchayat in Rupauli block under P.H.Division, Dhamdaha.
